eNCA's Lindsay Dentlinger is following developments. #DStv403 CAPE TOWN - Operation Dudula is set to launch in Cape Town on Saturday. The movement is on a nationwide campaign to root out undocumented migrants and put South Africans first. The DA, meanwhile, is calling on residents to reject and stand against the extension of the operation into the city. eNCA's Lindsay Dentlinger shares more details in the video above.